.SH SYNOPSIS
.B guix
\fI\,describe \/\fR[\fI\,OPTION\/\fR]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Display information about the channels currently in use.
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-format\fR=\fI\,FORMAT\/\fR
display information in the given FORMAT
.TP
\fB\-\-list\-formats\fR
display available formats
.TP
\fB\-p\fR, \fB\-\-profile\fR=\fI\,PROFILE\/\fR
display information about PROFILE
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
display this help and exit
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
display version information and exit
